<plot>Using radio-personality and cartoon-voice Arnold Stang as the expectant father, this entry in RKO's "This is America" series takes a look at the trials and tribulations faced by a father-to-be. The audience is taken to a special school in New York City where the new-fathers are taught how to handle---and change, when needed---the new baby. Stang carries this one beyond the usual "This is America" semi-documentary style.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?185513</url></doc>
